  "style_summary_en": "5-seat counter (single hinoki cypress board) near Sanjo Keihan Station, beside Niomon Gate.\nChef from Wakuden — maintains orthodox kaiseki ritual sequence with modern variations.\nDirect preparation at the counter.\n\nTabelog Gold 7 consecutive years.\nOne party of 6 per day — reservations full a year ahead.",
  "style_summary_jp": "三条京阪駅近く、仁王門横の5席カウンター（一枚板のヒノキ）。\n和久傳出身のシェフ — 正統懐石の儀礼的な流れを守りながらモダンな変奏を加える。\nカウンターで直接調理。\n\n食べログゴールド7年連続。\n1日1組6名様限定 — 1年先まで予約満席。",
  "holistic_signature_en": "Kyoto kaiseki modern realm — an elegant variation on the Wakuden lineage.",
  "holistic_signature_jp": "京都懐石モダン領域 — 和久傳系譜の魅力的な変奏。"
